thread.title: Susan Chung
thread.title_full: Ink Station reviewed by Susan Chung

author: Susan Chung
title: Susan Chung
text: I was disappointed when I put in the ink cartridge (cyan) in the printer and had not printed a few sheets and the ink level showed 1/4 used. Also the black cartridge did not print - all other colours were showed on the nozzle check but not the black in spite of putting and changing another new one.
